<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUS OF NAZARETH PASSED BY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Bang ahim mipi lung chawktho?
 Kintak taka vakviel haw chuh;
 Nichengin a chiehkawm zing ui,
 Banga mipi lung chawktho chuh?
 Mipi'n hiti hin a dawng ui,
 &quot;Nazareth Isu A chieh ahi&quot; (2)

[V2]
 2. Isu kiti hi kuo ahim?
 Bangdi'n em khawpi A sukling?
 Khuolzin vakviel mai in A thu'n,
 Mi thuzawh theihna A nei em?
 Mipi aw gi chun a gen hi,
 &quot;Nazareth Isu A chieh ahi&quot; (2)

[V3]
 3. Isu ahi khatvei hung kha,
 Mi banga um natna lakah;
 A chiehna mun chengah damlo -
 Bengngawng, kengbaite a pui ui.
 Mitduk, zie hen a kipak ui,
 &quot;Nazareth Isu A chieh ahi&quot; (2)

[V4]
 4. Gamtin muntin ah A chieh zel,
 A nung thiengtho I zui thei ui;
 I kawtkhak bul achun A ding,
 Kingainiem in cheng di'n A lut.
 Lawpin kiki lo ding I him?
 &quot;Nazareth Isu A chieh ahi&quot; (2)

[V5]
 5. Nanghaw, puokgik puote hung un,
 Ngaihdam lungmuon, chawlhna a um;
 Pa apat a vakvai nang haw,
 Hungun, A zahngaihna pawm un.
 Thepna thuokte, chawlhna a nai,
 &quot;Nazareth Isu A chieh ahi&quot; (2)

[V6]
 6. Mahleh A sapna niel zing a,
 A hehpih mak na matkhelh chun;
 Lungkhama hun kiheisan in,
 Na pauchamna ngaitha puona.
 &quot;A vaigei taluo tai&quot; tin au -
 &quot;Nazareth Isu A chieh zo tai&quot; (2)</lyrics>
<hymn_number>169</hymn_number>
</song>